review_text: Went inside the bank to cash a check written to my wife and met some of the most cheerful, courteous friendly and professional bank tellers it has been my good fortune to interact with. Even though I bank at a different location of this bank they verified that I was a First Horizon Bank customer and quickly cashed her check without having to jump through a lot of the hoops I have to do at other branches of this bank.
Treat people with a smile. What a bank should be.
